{
  "texts": [
    "In this section, we address RQ3, RQ4, and RQ5 posed in the introduction.",
    "The proposed SPICEPilot framework focuses on leveraging the capabilities of LLM to generate hardware SPICE code within a Python environment using PySpice, while avoiding the costly process of fine-tuning.",
    "Given the scarcity of data, the goal is to enable the LLM to reason and creatively contribute to the development of intelligent models in circuit design.",
    "This is achieved by embedding fundamental circuit logic, reasoning, and error identification mechanisms.",
    "In the SPICEPilot framework, we introduce a computationfriendly method that leverages a reference containing step-bystep guidelines for code generation."
  ]
}